  <brief_title>An Open-Label Rollover Study of Entecavir (BMS-200475) in Adults With Chronic Hepatitis B Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Rollover Study of Entecavir (BMS-200475) in Adults With Chronic Hepatitis B Infection Who Have Completed Previous Phase II Studies in Japan But Who Require Further Treatment</official_title>
