  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To provide open-label entecavir to subjects who have completed previous blinded entecavir
      trials in Japan and are assessed by the investigator as likely to benefit from additional
      anti-hepatitis B therapy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
